name: AQTIS
description: What is the project about? AQTIS is a smart liquidity protocol built around a AI-powered Quant technology layer. What makes your project unique? AQTIS has a solution for general liquidity issues many platforms and protocols have; one side is smart liquidity management by quant-tech and AI and the otherside the liquidity utilisation rate which is too low on deposited assets which results in relative low yield with high risk. The combination of these factors makes AQTIS a solid solution for general market liquidity problems. History of your project.
